name: ax-ros335
body: |- wral(s0, crp, wbr(cfv(cchp, cv(s0)), clt, co(co(nat1, cdp, cdp2(nat0, cdp2(nat3, cdp2(nat8, cdp2(nat8, nat3))))), cmul, cv(s0))))
comment: Theorem 12. of [RosserSchoenfeld] p. 71. Theorem ~ chpo1ubb states that the ` psi ` function is bounded by a linear term; this axiom postulates an upper bound for that linear term. This is stated as an axiom until a formal proof can be provided. (Contributed by Thierry Arnoux, 28-Dec-2021.)
